{"books":[{"id":"maoquanji29","name":"毛泽东全集第29卷","internal":false,"type":"pdf","official":false,"author":"张迪杰","files":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives0/main/maoquanji29.pdf"],"article":{"title":"给张有晋的信","alias":"","parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"给张有晋的信！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（1950年）遵嘱写了“船山学社”四字，未知可用否？此复，顺颂教祺。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"[1]1950年，张有晋与湖南教育界人士修建船山学社，纪念思想家王夫之。张有晋再次写信给毛主席，请他赐墨题写“船山学社”4个字。毛泽东欣然同意、挥笔题字，并回复：“遵嘱写了“船山学社’四字，未知可用否？此复，顺颂教祺。”"}],"authors":["毛泽东"],"dates":[{"year":1950}],"is_range_date":false,"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":498,"page_end":498},"tags":[{"name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"},{"type":"文稿类型","name":"书信"}]}]}